These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, pink
1. the person who likes pink is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Color   | pink | brown |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, water
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Beverage   | fanta | water |

 #################################

 
